                    <p class="mb-4 pb-2">Fag el-Gamous (which means Way of the Water Buffalo) is a large and important cemetery in Egypt that has been under archeological investigation (primarily by BYU researchers) for over 25 years. The excavation has garnered international attention because of the interesting insights gained by studying the Fag el-Gamous mummies.</p>
                    <div class="row g-4 mb-4 pb-3">
                        <div class="col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
